  ggplot(aes(x = as.factor(Week), y = `Win Percentage`, color = Picks))+
  geom_point()+
  geom_path(aes(x = Week))+
  geom_text_repel(aes(label=`Win Percentage`),hjust=0, vjust=0, size = 3)+

  ylim(c(0, 1)) +
  labs(x = "NFL Week", 
       y = "Correct Percentage",
       title = "Weekly Matched Correct Percentage")+
